{"tid":2329551,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"法國總統馬克龍確診武漢肺炎","createTime":"2020-12-17T09:48:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-17T09:48:30.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a519725cff8faa7e341445c941eb9b0ec37765dc","tid":2329551,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T09:48:30.000Z","msg":"新冠肺炎疫情大流行，法國總統馬克龍（Emmanuel Macron）確診感染新冠肺炎。<br />\n<br />\n彭博社報道指，愛舍麗宮發表聲明指，馬克龍在新冠肺炎檢測呈陽性，馬克龍需自我隔離7日，馬克龍期間會繼續工作。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2830000/2831299/XxjpsgC007013_20201211_PEPFN0A001_1024_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2830000%2F2831299%2FXxjpsgC007013_20201211_PEPFN0A001_1024_600.jpg&h=d6511416&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://topick.hket .com/article/2831299</code></pre>"}]}